text: Emma Margaret Marie Tachard-Mackey (born 4 January 1996) is a French-British actress. Since 2019, she has starred as Maeve Wiley in the Netflix comedy series Sex Education. Mackey was born in Le Mans. Her father is French and her mother is British. She graduated from the University of Leeds in 2016.
